text: The Salverda Omloop van de IJsseldelta is a women's staged cycle race which takes place in the Netherlands and is currently rated by the UCI as category 1.2, having previously been a national-level ranked event from 2009 to 2013.http://women.cyclingfever.com/stage.html?etappe_idd=MzQxOTA= ==Overall winners== ==References== Category:Women's cycle races Category:Cycle races in Belgium
